title: Everyday Sunday Discography 2002-2013 (6 Releases)
description:
--------------------------------------------------------------
EVERYDAY SUNDAY DISCOGRAPHY
--------------------------------------------------------------

This discography may or may not be complete.  It contains the following 6 releases...

 * 2002 - Stand Up
 * 2004 - Anthems for the Imperfect
 * 2007 - Wake Up! Wake Up!
 * 2009 - Best Night Of Our Lives
 * 2012 - Calculate - Single
 * 2013 - A New Beginning EP

Everyday Sunday is a band from Columbus, Ohio made up of Trey Pearson (founding member), Micah Kuiper, Tyler Craft, and Nick Spencer. The old band released two albums on Flicker Records including Stand Up and Anthems for the Imperfect. Wake Up! Wake Up! was the debut album on Inpop released May 22, 2007 on Inpop Records.

Be Blessed,
TorrentTracts - November 2013
